ComicInfo.Summary: Having left his homeland to journey to Oukoku, the Central State, Dark has now come face to face with Leen, the powerful Phantom Saint of the East Wind. Kyo's tantrums continue as she refuses to come to Dark's aid. Dark is in for a world of hurt as Leen's followers, Chao and Tou, arrive at the side of their mistress. Just then four magic orbs that Leen possesses circle Dark ominously. Dark jumps feet first into battle!
